name: My wonderland 2
description: In this collection, I introduce you a land which has no rules or obstacles and you can find out whatever you imagine there. You are going to meet the girls who live in my wonderland. Be ready guys! cause you’re gonna fall in love and wanna have one of them. My girls are gorgeous and also DIFFERENT. Cause they have attractive hair which are made of nature. Yes, you’ve heard right. Also these girls have special hairstyles in various ceremonies. If you wanna know why I started this collection, I can say that in our world we always see special fashion models with special hairstyles but in this collection I illustrated different or maybe weird hairstyles. Imagine a girl with hair made of flowers...
